## DINGDING MCP
基于 Model Context Protocol (MCP) 的钉钉推送。


## 工具列表
| name | description |
| ----------- | ----------- |
| auth  | key验证 |
| push | 推送消息 |

## MCP 服务器配置
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "dingding": {
      "isActive": true,
      "name": "calculator",
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "uv",
      "args": [
        "--directory",
        "/Users/xiezi/explore/mcp-dingding/src",  # 替换为自己的路径
        "run",
        "-m",
        "mcp_dingding"
      ]
      }
  }
}

{
  "mcpServers": {
    "mcp_dingding": {
        "command": "uvx",
        "args": [
          "mcp_dingding@latest"
        ]
      }
  }
}
```

